  "keyFeatures": [
    "60+ modern controls implementing Fluent Design (NavigationView, TabView, TreeView, ColorPicker, InfoBar, TeachingTip, and more)",
    "Full Fluent Design System support with light/dark theme resources and compact mode",
    "Accessible controls with built-in AutomationPeer implementations",
    "Cross-architecture support: x86, x64, ARM64",
    "Ships as part of the Windows App SDK (WinAppSDK) via NuGet",
    "XAML-based declarative UI with C# and C++/WinRT bindings",
    "Experimental/Preview API pipeline for community feedback before stable release",
    "WinUI 3 Gallery interactive sample app available on the Microsoft Store"
